            <h2>Multi-Custodian Model</h2>
            <p>We never put all our gold in one shoebox. We use multiple "baskets" (Banks).</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Diversification:</strong> We spread the wealth across different top banks.</li>
                <li><strong>Best of Breed:</strong> Bank A is good at cash, Bank B is good at gold. We get both!</li>
            </ul>
            <div class="fun-fact">Analogy: It's like having a master key to the best vaults in the world.</div>
